Kind: captions
Language: uz

00:00:00.700 --> 00:00:03.920
 fontFamily atributidan siz 

00:00:03.920 --> 00:00:05.330
 TextView shriftni o‘rnatish uchun foydalanasiz.

00:00:05.330 --> 00:00:08.045
Biz shrift Sans Serif Light bo‘lishinixohlaymiz,

00:00:08.045 --> 00:00:12.620
sans-serif-light qiymatini fontFamily atributiga o‘rnatamiz.

00:00:12.620 --> 00:00:15.401
Buni biroz aniqroq qilish uchun,
sizga Android Studio da ko‘rsatishga ijozat bering.

00:00:16.720 --> 00:00:19.920
Xo‘sh, men bu erga qaytib keldim -
sevimli activity_main.xml fayliga

00:00:19.920 --> 00:00:21.180
keling, yana bir nechta atributlarni qo‘shaylik.

00:00:22.350 --> 00:00:26.080
"Tug‘ilgan kuningiz bilan, Ben" TextView dan boshlamoqchiman.

00:00:26.080 --> 00:00:32.530
Men qo‘shayotgan atribut - android: fontFamily .

00:00:32.530 --> 00:00:36.950
OK va men istagan shrift, agar siz eslasangiz, bu 

00:00:36.950 --> 00:00:43.500
 Sans Serif Light .

00:00:43.500 --> 00:00:47.560
Va har doimgidek, u qo‘shtirnoq orasida.

00:00:47.560 --> 00:00:49.340
Endi buni ko‘rish biroz qiyin,
lekin

00:00:49.340 --> 00:00:53.170
tasvir yangilanganda ko‘rishimiz mumkin 
ingichka, San Serif Light shriftini.

00:00:54.200 --> 00:00:57.470
Agar siz TextView dan boshqa joyni bossangiz, buni yaxshiroq ko‘rishingiz mumkin

00:00:57.470 --> 00:01:00.620
va quyidagicha taqqoslashingiz mumkin, bu eski shrift va

00:01:00.620 --> 00:01:01.369
bu yangi shrift.

00:01:02.460 --> 00:01:05.330
E’tibor beradigan va siz uchun muammo bo‘lishi mumkin bir-ikki narsa.

00:01:06.360 --> 00:01:09.400
Bu yerda narsalar defis bilan ajratilgan,
quyi chiziq bilan emas.

00:01:09.400 --> 00:01:11.650
Siz shu tarzda qilishingizga ishonch hosil qiling
bu to‘g‘ri.

00:01:11.650 --> 00:01:15.350
"sans-serif-light"ni ham to‘g‘ri yozganingizga ishonch hosil qiling.

00:01:15.350 --> 00:01:16.100
Masalan,

00:01:16.100 --> 00:01:20.590
kompyuter pastki chiziqlar bilan "sans_serif_light" kabi yozilgan qiymatni tanimaydi.

00:01:20.590 --> 00:01:23.530
Bu yerda ko‘rishingiz mumkin
eski shriftga qaytdi.

00:01:23.530 --> 00:01:26.622
Shuni ham yodda tutingki, matn ustida yurganingizda, ushbu xabarni olishingiz mumkin.

00:01:26.622 --> 00:01:33.418
"Attribute fontFamily is only used in API
level 16 and higher, current min is 15".

00:01:33.418 --> 00:01:38.044
Eslasangiz, loyihada biz SDK minimal miqdorini 15 ga o‘rnatdik,

00:01:38.044 --> 00:01:39.440
yoki "Ice Cream Sandwich".

00:01:40.490 --> 00:01:45.180
Bu anglatadi, bu atributini ishlatish
uchun sizga bitta yuqoriroq versiya kerak.

00:01:45.180 --> 00:01:46.430
Bu juda katta muammo emas, 

00:01:46.430 --> 00:01:50.360
bu degani, bu matn eski telefonlarda

00:01:50.360 --> 00:01:54.222
eski chunkier shriftida va yangi telefonlarda
 Sans Serif Light shriftida ko‘rinadi.

00:01:54.222 --> 00:01:59.770
OK, shuning uchun men davom etaman va
boshqa TextView ga atribut qo‘shaman.

00:01:59.770 --> 00:02:00.458
Keling, pastga tushaylik.

00:02:00.458 --> 00:02:05.370
 android: fontFamily .

00:02:05.370 --> 00:02:08.419
OK, hozir Preview ekranida
hamma narsa to‘g‘ri ko‘rinadi, lekin

00:02:08.419 --> 00:02:10.430
uni har doim telefoningizda ishga tushirib ko‘ring.

00:02:10.430 --> 00:02:11.446
Yashil "Run" tugmachasini bosaman.

00:02:11.446 --> 00:02:14.250
va million yil kutaman.

00:02:14.250 --> 00:02:17.502
Men telefonni uraman,
OK ga urmoqchiman.

00:02:17.502 --> 00:02:20.210
Yaxshi, va uni telefoningizga yuklaganingizda

00:02:20.210 --> 00:02:24.210
ingichka Sans Serif Light shriftida ozgina narsa.

00:02:24.210 --> 00:02:26.380
Zo‘r ish, ikkitasi bo‘ldi,
uchtasi oldinda.

